# 2. 🧠 Liquidity System Architecture

The liquidity system consists of three core components:

* PNJC Token Contract
* Liquidity Pools (Uniswap / Quickswap AMM)
* PNJC_Free_Router execution layer

---

## 2.1 System Flow Diagram

```
Token Allocation
      ↓
Vesting Unlock
      ↓
Circulating Supply
      ↓
Liquidity Provision (LP)
      ↓
DEX Pool (AMM)
      ↓
Trading Execution via Router
      ↓
Market Price Discovery
```

